{"lastModified":1775133582930,"uri":"c::10120242293::vessel::673eef60-5668-11ef-a8a2-ed728478bcf0","yachtType":["Catamaran","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nWelcome aboard Serenity, luxurious Lagoon 52F, completely refitted in 2023, that combines exceptional performance with unmatched comfort. Whether you're enjoying the expansive cockpit lounge for a morning coffee or sipping wine under the stars, Serenity promises a truly indulgent getaway.\n\nWith five elegant double cabins, each with its own en-suite, Serenity offers unparalleled accommodation for up to 10 guests. The spacious living areas, both inside and out, create the perfect environment for relaxation and connection, while the stunning teak deck and swim platform invite you to embrace the beauty of the open sea.\n\nSerenity is equipped with state-of-the-art amenities including a new galley, luxurious upholstery, and an array of water toys to keep you entertained. Her expert crew is on hand to provide exceptional service, ensuring your time aboard is both peaceful and exhilarating.\n\nFrom the expansive flybridge with sunbathing areas to the electric swimming platform, Serenity offers the perfect blend of relaxation, adventure, and sophistication.\n\nThe name Serenity evokes a sense of calm, peace, and tranquility, perfectly reflecting the yacht’s luxurious and relaxing environment. It signifies a peaceful escape on the water, where guests can unwind, rejuvenate, and experience pure harmony in every moment of their journey.","blueprint":{"name":"SERENITY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::673eef60-5668-11ef-a8a2-ed728478bcf0::assets::f78e2e90-fdd0-11ef-af25-67bf389db7d4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::673eef60-5668-11ef-a8a2-ed728478bcf0::assets::f78c0bb0-fdd0-11ef-891b-73e8b41036b9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::673eef60-5668-11ef-a8a2-ed728478bcf0::assets::f78d6b40-fdd0-11ef-af24-67bf389db7d4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::67